text: The Bellas are ready to get back in the ring
title: The Bellas are ready to get back in the ring

meta_data.description: Appearing on "E! News," Nikki and Brie Bella reflect on the most recent season of Total Bellas, prepare for their future - including a potential in-ring return - and are ready for the premiere of the newest season of Total Divas, Wednesday, Nov. 1, at 9/8 C on E!.
